<head>
	<title>课件-标题</title>
    <meta name="author" content="Hong Liu" />

    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="0" http-equiv="expires" />
    <meta content="no-cache" http-equiv="cache-control" />
    <meta content="no-cache" http-equiv="pragma" />
    <meta content="on" http-equiv="cleartype" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" name="viewport" />
    <meta content="True" name="HandheldFriendly" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />

    <style>
        .componentContainer {
            position: absolute;
            line-height: normal;
        }
        .transformContainer {
            -webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;
			-moz-transform-origin: 0 0;
			-o-transform-origin: 0 0;
			-ms-transform-origin: 0 0;
			transform-origin: 0 0;
        }
        .bg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="present_dependence/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href='present_dependence/css/web-fonts.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' />
    <link href='styles/app/themes/backgroundClasses.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico" />

	<script type="text/javascript" src="present_dependence/scripts/impress.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="impress-not-supported">
    <!-- This is a work around / hack to get the user's browser to download the fonts
 if they decide to save the presentation. -->
    <div style="visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px">
        <img src="present_dependence/css/Lato-Bold.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/Lato-BoldItalic.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/Lato-Regular.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/hei.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/song.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/kai.woff" />
        <img src="present_dependence/css/weibei.woff" />
    </div>
    <div class="fallback-message">
        <p>你的浏览器 <b>缺少本软件运行所需的功能。</b> 现在本软件运行在简单视图下。</p>
        <p>为了获得更好的体验，请下载最新版的 <b>Chrome</b>, <b>Safari</b> 或 <b>Firefox</b> 浏览器.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg">
        <div id="impress">
            {{#slides.models}} {{#attributes}}
            <div class="step" data-x="1" data-y="1">
                <div class="{{background}}" style="width: {{width}}; height: {{height}}">
                    {{#components}} {{#renderComponent .}}{{/renderComponent}} {{/components}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/attributes}} {{/slides.models}}
            {{!-- <div id="overview" class="step active" data-x="1" data-y="1" data-scale="9"></div> --}}
        </div>
        <div class="hint">
            <p>请用 空格 或 <-|-> 来浏览幻灯片</p>
        </div>

        <script>
            if ("ontouchstart" in document.documentElement) {
                document.querySelector(".hint").innerHTML =
                    "<p>按 <- 和 -> 来翻页</p>";
            }
        </script>
        {{#interval}}
        <script>
            var interval = {{.}};
            if (interval >= 1000) {
                setInterval(function () {
                    pres().next();
                }, interval);
            }
        </script>
        {{/interval}}
    </div>
    <script>
        if (!window.presStarted) {
			startPres(document, window);
			pres().init();
        }
    </script>
</body>
